ology and Mapman enriched terms, as well as tissue- and\ncondition-specific patterns of gene expression within the module. Furthermore,\nthe database features interactive network visualisation via CytoscapeWeb. VTCdb\nshould aid researchers in their prioritization of gene candidates for further\nstudy towards the understanding of biological processes related to many aspects\nof grapevine development and metabolism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 May 2013 13:15:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-20"}
